HEADWORD: echo chamber
<hw>ech"o cham"ber</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Music,
broadcasting)</fld> <def>A room with walls that resonate sound,
producing audible echoes; it is used especially to create special sound
effects in recording music.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

